prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon raccoon wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, looking slightly guilty with its paws covered in cake frosting, cheekily peeking over the top of a giant, beautifully decorated birthday cupcake that is missing a large bite. The text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script across the middle of the cupcake. The entire scene is rendered in a delightful watercolor painting style, featuring soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds at the edges. Flat 2D artwork. --ar 5:7
prompts.backCover: A single, tiny splotch of colorful cake frosting in the upper-left corner, as if accidentally left by a finger. The background is a plain, off-white paper texture. This is a very minimalist design. The image is rendered in a watercolor painting style with soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds at the edges. Flat 2D artwork. --ar 5:7
prompts.leftInterior: A gentle cascade of colorful confetti and delicate streamers drifting down from the top of the frame against a soft, textured paper background. The confetti pieces are simple geometric shapes in pastel shades, matching a celebratory theme. The entire scene is rendered in a delightful watercolor painting style, featuring soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds at the edges, creating a festive yet subtle pattern. Flat 2D artwork. --ar 5:7
prompts.rightInterior: A minimalist decorative border along the bottom edge of the card, featuring a simple, elegant swirl of colorful watercolor paint, reminiscent of frosting, accented with a few scattered pieces of tiny, matching confetti. The majority of the space is a clean, off-white paper texture, leaving ample room for a personal message. The artwork is rendered in a watercolor painting style with soft, flowing colors and visible artistic brush strokes. Flat 2D artwork. --ar 5:7
